{"tid":818325,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台女港鐵大戰中國客　最後灰機：香港人好唔團結！","createTime":"2018-09-14T04:34:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T04:35:11.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"54556e5b9470fd56d39509f7dc031246e67d27eb","tid":818325,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T04:34:07.000Z","msg":"如果有三個人，但港鐵車廂得番兩個位，你會唔會照坐落去？近日有位居港台女喺港鐵見到三名成年內地人坐兩個位，就叫佢哋唔好咁做。點知⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n由台灣來港生活幾年嘅李小姐，喺地鐵就睇唔過眼幾個內地人嘅行為，所以拍片放上Facebook群組「North District 北區」：「好聲好氣講又唔聽，係要搞到咁，其他人喺度食花生，最心灰的係隔離個香港男人起身之後叫我哋慢慢玩，鬧完再返番嚟坐」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/-2018-09-12-12.58.36_3073610615b989d421c12e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F-2018-09-12-12.58.36_3073610615b989d421c12e.png&h=40497631&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事情是咁的，一男兩女操普通話嘅內地乘客喺坐東鐵綫時，就三個人坐兩個位，搞到其他人擠逼難受。台女李小姐就叫佢哋唔好咁做啦，但個內地女就話「我們三個人坐一點點，我們三個人坐兩個位，對吧？」仲叫台女唔好坐！咩思維&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n港男閃人<br />\n<br />\n「唔怕醜吖嘛！唔緊要」「你拍什麼呀！」雙方爭拗期間，坐喺台女同內地客中間嘅港男決定閃人，仲話：「你哋慢慢玩」、「唔好影到我」。個內地男人隨即大笑，搞到好似係台女做錯咁&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n附近不少乘客仲喺度笑，台女表示「港男唔幫拖就算仲要踩一腳」，嘆道「香港人真係唔團結」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/-2018-09-12-1.12.12_11663569485b98a070f1221.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F-2018-09-12-1.12.12_11663569485b98a070f1221.png&h=0aeb8d2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/2018-09-12-1.14.00_12775550205b98a12cbfaef_20808842515b9959a63a3e0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F2018-09-12-1.14.00_12775550205b98a12cbfaef_20808842515b9959a63a3e0.jpg&h=cc2d175f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/-2018-09-12-1.14.50_15922153155b98a13083d36.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F-2018-09-12-1.14.50_15922153155b98a13083d36.png&h=d4b688c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.orientalsunday.hk/300674/%e6%bd%ae%e8%81%9e/%e5%8f%b0%e5%a5%b3-%e6%b8%af%e9%90%b5-%e5%85%a7%e5%9c%b0%e4%ba%ba-%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e4%ba%ba/7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.orientalsunday.hk%2F300674%2F%25e6%25bd%25ae%25e8%2581%259e%2F%25e5%258f%25b0%25e5%25a5%25b3-%25e6%25b8%25af%25e9%2590%25b5-%25e5%2585%25a7%25e5%259c%25b0%25e4%25ba%25ba-%25e9%25a6%2599%25e6%25b8%25af%25e4%25ba%25ba%2F7%2F&d=9n63ACnIhs93NpSLY7Y4xzANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=dafa940a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.orientalsunday.hk/300674/%e6%bd%ae%e8%81%9e/%e5%8f%b0%e5%a5%b3-%e6%b8%af%e9%90%b5-%e5%85%a7%e5%9c%b0%e4%ba%ba-%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e4%ba%ba/7/</a>"},{"pid":"8b2bb02ca9c160e54369f31136a3900550ebb9a3","tid":818325,"uid":103921,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T04:35:11.000Z","msg":"現場有冇鍵盤先？"}]}